{
 "name": "RPlog_Blizzard_Baby",
 "title": "Blizzard Baby",
 "summary": "In the NR Embassy housing wing in Plaxton City, the heavily pregnant ambassador Ambrosia waits miserably in her quarters amid swirling political rumors as her labor begins. Her husband Tivadar returns from an errand to find her in the early throes, and despite her stubborn insistence that she has no time to give birth, he gently coaxes her toward the hospital, their protocol droid C4 dragging an overpacked bag behind them. They brave the cold, blustery drive to Dr. Tarquin Memorial Hospital, where, many hours later in the maternity ward, Ambrosia rages against the cold and the pain while Tivadar endures her crushing grip and offers what soothing words he can. After a long, exhausting labor, the scene closes as a shrill newborn's cry finally pierces the air.",
